Read Me

Install python
Install pyCharm IDE
You would need bunch of python packages! Install or follow the steps

mkdir my_ai_agent
cd my_ai_agent
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate # On Windows: .\venv\Scripts\activate
pip install langchain-community langchain-openai python-dotenv # or langchain-google-genai for Gemini
Create a .env file in your my_ai_agent directory.

Add your API key:

OPENAI_API_KEY="your_openai_api_key_here"
# OR
GOOGLE_API_KEY="your_google_api_key_here"
